snippet.title: Modern Warships — PC Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Download here: https://modernwarships.com/

Gaijin Entertainment and Artstorm studio are pleased to announce that the open beta testing of the PC version of Modern Warships has already started. The game's official website has been launched, and the Gaijin.Net store has started selling unique premium pioneer kits for players who will join Modern Warships' large-scale naval battles at the very start of the OBT. 

Download Modern Warships
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.Shooter.ModernWarships&hl=ru&gl=US
Appstore: https://apps.apple.com/ae/app/modern-warships-naval-battles/id1541751298
Huawei: https://appgallery.huawei.com/#/app/C104642661

https://discord.gg/modernwarships

#modernwarships #mw
